<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Your privacy is important to us. This privacy statement explains the personal data GBC Ticketing processes, how we process it, and for what purposes.</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>When you purchase tickets as a guest, we collect:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Your name</li>
    <li>Your email address</li>
    <li>Purchase details (events, quantities, dates)</li>
</ul>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>We use your information to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Process your ticket purchases</li>
    <li>Send purchase confirmations</li>
    <li>Communicate event details</li>
</ul>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>
<p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us.</p>